  "title": "Aspects | Origins Addon",
  "description": "An element-based Origins addon",
  "body": "\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6uFjYV3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"390\" height=\"125\" /></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AfoiG6x.png\" alt=\"Requirements\" width=\"315\" height=\"46\" /> </strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Fabric API\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fabric API</a> | <a title=\"Origins\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/origins/\">Origins</a> | <a title=\"Origins Extra Keybinds\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/origins-extra-keybinds\">Origins Extra Keybinds</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Intended to contribute to Minecraft's combat system, along with adding features that feel a bit more unique than the regular Origins that are out there, with types falling under the aspects.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[ ! ] Currently, as this project is new, it is open to discussion and change.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Please join the Discord for support.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;(Also on <a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/aspects-origins-addon\">CurseForge</a>)</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h5 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Overview</strong></h5>\n<p>When you first join the game, you are taken to the Aspect selection screen. Each Aspect has its respective upsides and downsides. Your choice of Aspect determines your options for the second choice layer, the Types.</p>\n<p><strong>&gt; Required on both the server and client</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<h5 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Resources</strong></h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Discord</strong></span>: <strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/p533EcFTSx\">https://discord.gg/p533EcFTSx</a></span><br /></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Github:</strong> <a href=\"https://github.com/Fishplex/Aspects\">https://github.com/Fishplex/Aspects<br /></a></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Issue Tracker: <a href=\"https://github.com/Fishplex/Aspects/issues\">https://github.com/Fishplex/Aspects/issues</a></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Wiki: <a href=\"https://github.com/Fishplex/Aspects/wiki\">https://github.com/Fishplex/Aspects/wiki</a></span></strong><a href=\"https://github.com/Fishplex/Aspects/wiki\"><br /></a><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Trello:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/N2qwbnWr/to-do\">https://trello.com/b/N2qwbnWr/to-do</a></strong> </span></h5>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you'd like to contact me directly, please do so through Curseforge or add the creator on Discord at <strong>foxglove#5663</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q523aAN.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"258\" height=\"243\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D1tTqkg.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"266\" height=\"240\" /></p>",
